{"tid":722070,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"感覺做咗邊緣人。","createTime":"2018-06-29T07:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T07:52:18.000Z","uid":77132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"03da611f3fb1063e3bc95c5ad03757534958eeb6","tid":722070,"uid":77132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T07:32:45.000Z","msg":"朋友方面都唔知做乜，唉 有啲咩聚會都冇叫我<br />\n感情方面根本不值一提。<br />\n自從分手之後大病一場，做啲咩事都唔順利而家好似做咗透明人冇人記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生日都冇乜人記得慶祝屋企人都冇幫我慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，係有親戚咁啱生日先順手幫我慶祝埋（蛋糕牌無我個名）都冇咩人會關心我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同你傾計都係想八卦嘢"},{"pid":"c15fc08cf9850c890db6336d3cf370644650a183","tid":722070,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T07:35:24.000Z","msg":"&infin;．&deg;。那些沒有愛情的日子，原來是最無憂無慮的。*--☆!!&nbsp;"},{"pid":"c1c634e54df6d4283d271aa7075d831c1b99940d","tid":722070,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c15fc08cf9850c890db6336d3cf370644650a183","tid":722070,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T07:35:24.000Z","msg":"&infin;．&deg;。那些沒有愛情的日子，原來是最無憂無慮的。*--☆!!&nbsp;"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T07:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/154218_1f61dc1b3e2cde6102eba86cc00171b4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F154218_1f61dc1b3e2cde6102eba86cc00171b4.gif&h=0ca9bce7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcfd8bafeb76b430bd2f7347e224f585bc8d6ad5","tid":722070,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1c634e54df6d4283d271aa7075d831c1b99940d","tid":722070,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c15fc08cf9850c890db6336d3cf370644650a183","tid":722070,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":